## What is Solid Cache?

Solid Cache is Rails 8's default caching solution. It uses your database instead of Redis.

**Key Benefits:**
- ✅ No Redis dependency
- ✅ Uses database with optimized queries
- ✅ Automatic cache expiration
- ✅ Supports all Rails cache features
- ✅ Proven at scale (HEY, Basecamp)
- ✅ Works with PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite

